data.description: A Mid-Century Modern Gem centrally located in South Buckhead and Midtown just steps to the Northside Beltline.  Don't miss this opportunity to live in the vibrant heart of the city just minutes to restaurants, shopping, walking trails, playgrounds, quick I85 & I75 interstate access, 15 minutes from the airport and walk to Bobby Jones golf and Bitsy Grant tennis center. Brookwood Park is located on rare lush acreage in a park-like setting and features a swimming pool, tennis courts, koi pond, garden area, grilling, an on-site manager, gated parking and abundant guest parking. The residence is spacious with an oversized great room, updated kitchen and bath, featuring gorgeous custom cabinets and stone counter tops. A bright and sunny glass-enclosed veranda off of both large bedrooms is ideal for a home office, an additional den or home gym.  Abundant storage throughout the unit! A central laundry room is located in the building. Lease permits are available after one year of ownership. WELCOME HOME! Several photos in this listing are virtually staged.
